{"title":"读《花》二绝","authors":["董必武"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":5,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"读《花》二绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董必武"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年承曹靖华同志赠所著散文集《花》，读未半，得小诗一首；读毕又得一首。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿花常好月常圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻景于今现眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁若水仙幽若菊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅香暗动骨弥坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已见好花常在世，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更期圆月照中天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢庄作赋惟形象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿否同名喻续篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年四月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}